incident_updates.body: We are currently experiencing an ongoing incident. We have determined the origin of the issue affecting our Dedicated Servers offer on the specific rack. Here are some supplementary details : Start time : 22/11/2025 21:08 UTC Impacted Service(s) : All servers in the rack 23A23 are temporarily unavailable. Customers Impact : Customers are temporarily unable to access and use their servers in the specified rack. Root Cause : This incident is caused by an electrical equipment issue. Ongoing Actions : The incident has been identified and our teams are mobilised to restore service as quickly as possible. We will keep you updated on the progress and resolution. We apologize for any inconvenience caused and appreciate your understanding.
